name: Tiger VC DAO & Consensus Limited Edition NFT Pass

metadata.description:
Tiger VC DAO is jointly initiated by a number of early Crypto practitioners, well-known VCs, Crypto investment research experts and industry opinion leaders. It aims to establish a decentralized VC that belongs to everyone at a time when centralized VCs continue to monopolize cryptocurrency investment opportunities.  Give everyone an equal opportunity to invest in crypto.

A limited amount of PASS is launched for Consensus participants. Holders of this joint PASS can enjoy the following rights:
1. The whitelist qualification of the latest NFT of Tiger VC DAO
2.Tiger VC DAO global high-quality project participation opportunities
3. High-quality project library and research report subscription and learning opportunities;
4. Private investment research channel, regularly communicate with global high-quality investment research experts and well-known VCs every week.
